Package io.helidon.common

Class CollectionsHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.helidon.common.CollectionsHelper
  • public abstract class CollectionsHelper
extends Object
    A set of static methods similar to Java9's List.of(), Set.of() and Map.of().
